body:
I run into the same problem when updating my codebase from 1.0-alpha to the current nightly.
Possibly a duplicate of #21212.

I've just ran into this myself. The code is a little hefty to share, but I've included the stack trace below. Looks as though it's crashing upon some kind of recursion while matching the assoc type's where clause?

It seems my rustc is a few days behind, i'll update now and post again if the update fixes the issue.

rustc 1.0.0-nightly (92ff8ea52 2015-01-27 23:08:13 +0000)
